OL,3,C250 jobs at risk as UK's largest glass
OL,4,Cfactory set to close
OL,6,FMore than 250 jobs have been put at
OL,7,Frisk as trade unions and local
OL,8,Fpoliticans warn the largest fibre
OL,9,Fglass factory in the UK is set to
OL,10,Fclose.
OL,12,FThe NEG Nippon Electric Glass Fiber
OL,13,FWorks (EGFU), based at Hindley Green
OL,14,Fnear Wigan, has been owned by the
OL,15,FJapanese company since 2016 and was a
OL,16,Fmajor part of their planned expansion
OL,17,Finto the European market.
