OL,3,C250 jobs at risk as UK's largest glass
OL,4,Cfactory set to close
OL,6,FThe future of the site has been in
OL,7,Fdoubt since April, when NEG announced
OL,8,Fthey were looking for a buyer to take
OL,9,Fover their UK branch.
OL,11,FAt a Board of Directors meeting held
OL,12,Fon Wednesday 18 June, the company's
OL,13,Fpresident Akira Kishimoto announced
OL,14,Fthey would "cease operations" of their
OL,15,FUK subsidiary.
OL,17,FThe President confirmed the site will
OL,18,F"stop its production in late June".
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/7
