OL,3,C250 jobs at risk as UK's largest glass
OL,4,Cfactory set to close
OL,6,FDespite working with the company to
OL,7,Ffind a new owner, Labour MP for
OL,8,FMakerfield Josh Simons has published
OL,9,Fan open letter to workers in which he
OL,10,Fsays that "Nippon is unwilling to do a
OL,11,Fdeal to secure the future of this site
OL,12,Fand your jobs."
OL,14,FHe said: "I am angry and I will stand
OL,15,Fup for you in the coming days to
OL,16,Fsecure whatever support I can for you
OL,17,Fand your families.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/7
