OL,6,F"I want you to know that I value and
OL,7,Frespect the work you do. I care very
OL,8,Fmuch about doing my absolute best for
OL,9,Fyou, for this community, and for
OL,10,Findustry in the UK.
OL,12,F"In this age of insecurity, it matters
OL,13,Fwhere things are made and who makes
OL,14,Fthem, and I will push for this site
OL,15,Fand Hindley Green to be at the front
OL,16,Fof the queue for future investment
OL,17,Fopportunities."
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G4/7
