OL,3,C250 jobs at risk as UK's largest glass
OL,4,Cfactory set to close
OL,6,FGMB Regional Organiser Gary Edwards
OL,7,Fdescribed the decision to close the
OL,8,Fsight as "deeply disappointing" and a
OL,9,F"bitter betrayal of workers and UK
OL,10,Findustry".
OL,12,FMr Simons has been working with the
OL,13,FGovernment, the GMB Union, and
OL,14,Fprospective buyers to secure the
OL,15,Ffuture of the sight, but said NEG
OL,16,Frepeatedly changed their conditions
OL,17,Ffor any sale with little notice.
OL,19,FHe said: "I am so sorry that we
OL,20,Fcouldn't get this over the line. I
OL,21,Fknow how anxious this period has been.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G5/7
