OL,6,F"I have spoken to many of you in
OL,7,Frecent weeks, as have Gary and your
OL,8,Flocal councillors, and I can only
OL,9,Fimagine how you feel. I want you to
OL,10,Fknow that your work is a source of
OL,11,Fpride for me, for this area, and for
OL,12,Fthe country."
OL,14,FGary Edwards added: "Everyone involved
OL,15,Fworked tirelessly to try and secure
OL,16,Fthe site's future.
OL,18,F"But for every solution we found, the
OL,19,Fcompany presented another problem. It
OL,20,Fbecame hard not to question how
OL,21,Fserious they were about doing a deal."
