OL,6,FMr Simons went on to invite workers to
OL,7,Fa meeting at the local Labour club
OL,8,Fwith representatives of the GMB union,
OL,9,Fwhere he promised to explain what had
OL,10,Fhappened and explain the next steps
OL,11,Fthey could take.
